    "description_long": "This is a modern grave site featuring a polished black granite headstone with a vertical rectangular shape, set atop a raised, rectangular stone base. The headstone is inscribed with text and a cross motif, and the grave is bordered by a light gray stone platform that extends around the perimeter. A small potted plant is placed adjacent to the headstone, adding a touch of greenery to the otherwise somber design. The grave cover is made of a lighter, speckled stone, contrasting with the dark headstone. The overall appearance is clean, well-maintained, and typical of contemporary cemetery plots.",
